mixin welcome
  div.splash
      h1 Contribute
      p We're testing out new ways to help the community build new tools and solve problems together.
  div
      div.content.content-contrast.is-center
          div.l-box-lrg.pure-u-1.pure-u-med-1-2.pure-u-lrg-1-3
              h1.content-subhead
                i.fa.fa-link
              h3.content-subhead What we're doing
              p
                | We're studying how to help the community partner together to solve problems and build new tools. We've curated code projects you can get involved in.
            div.l-box-lrg.pure-u-1.pure-u-med-1-2.pure-u-lrg-1-3
              h1.content-subhead
                i.fa.fa-users
              h3.content-subhead How you can help
              p
                | This is open to all! There's something for designers, developers, scientists, communicators and all our contributors.
            div.l-box-lrg.pure-u-1.pure-u-med-1-2.pure-u-lrg-1-3
              h1.content-subhead
                i.fa.fa-heart
              h3.content-subhead Open & Sharing
              p
                | On openness and sharing... more text on open and maybe a link to a page. Legal stuffs.



